ISLAMABAD, Apr 20 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain Tuesday strongly condemned the assassination attempt on senior journalist Absar Alam.
In a tweet, he said that police had been asked to immediately investigate the incident and details would be released to the media as soon as they come to light.
